yet you got hurt cutting fruit?

7
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,920
Mr. Song, where's the wound?

8
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,680
It healed.

9
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,840
I'm so strong.

10
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:29,719
Even my blood clots faster.

11
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,752
What are you doing?

12
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,280
To do the design.

13
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:39,439
You're showing
a dizzy old man in his fifties

14
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,640
this spinning 3D design?

15
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,599
So what are you suggesting, Mr. Song?

16
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:55,879
Create a hand-drawn 3D model for Mr. Yu.

17
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:56,640
Good idea.

18
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,599
You've relied on software so long,
you've forgotten basic sketching?

19
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,840
I need a tutorial.

20
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,560
No need. I'll teach you.

21
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:35,759
Focus on drawing.

22
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,159
I didn't mean to, Mr. Song.

23
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:44,879
Does it hurt?

24
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,479
Yes.

25
00:03:50,624 --> 00:03:56,800
ظآزNothing more, nothing less,
just like thisظآز

26
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,240
I'll be gentler.

27
00:04:04,896 --> 00:04:08,480
ظآزI am safe, I am soundظآز

28
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:11,720
ظآزInside your armsظآز

29
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:18,560
ظآزTurn around, turn aroundظآز

30
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,920
Does this count as a work injury?

31
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,639
What do you want?

32
00:04:26,944 --> 00:04:32,960
ظآزTurn around, turn aroundظآز

33
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,528
Help me shower tonight.

34
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:49,520
ظآزYou're nothing but beautiful
in my eyesظآز

35
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,560
You're hurting me.

36
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,079
Sorry.

37
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,439
Don't use the towel.

38
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,959
It'll chafe.

39
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:10,399
Use your hands.

40
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,399
Does it still hurt?

41
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:40,759
Of all my scars,
this one is my favorite.

42
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:45,000
Because you gave it to me.

43
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,000
Ji Xuan.

44
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,639
Mr. Song, what are you doing here?

45
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,879
Can't sleep. Just want to chat.

46
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,800
Are you settling in okay?

47
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,439
I'm fine.

48
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,519
No sleep night before last.

49
00:06:38,879 --> 00:06:39,759
No sleep last night.

50
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:42,600
And tonight, I still can't sleep.

51
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,879
Won't you ask me

52
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,040
why I can't sleep?

53
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,519
Wh-why?

54
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:59,079
Because I'm used to my own bed.

55
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,240
Then I'll sleep in the guest room.

56
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,439
No need for that.

57
00:07:05,312 --> 00:07:06,240
Let's sleep together.

58
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:07,639
Song Zhaoli.

59
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:09,920
How about

60
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:13,600
