61
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,279
You can't escape, Ji Xuan.

62
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:23,879
I will claim that title.

63
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:32,240
(Song, Mr. Yu booked a flight
for tonight.)

64
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,720
(He'll likely leave here early.)

65
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,160
- Mr. Yu.
- Mr. Yu.

66
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:39,968
Where are you going?

67
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:42,240
The weather's turning. Tsunami's coming.

68
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:45,639
Mr. Yu, we know
you're seeking designers for that land.

69
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:48,560
