78
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,680
Why not let me try harder?

79
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,199
You think blocking him shows sincerity?

80
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,759
Or chasing after him?

81
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,480
Are you saying...

82
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,639
Mr. Yu can leave, and we can follow.

83
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:23,040
But we need him to know

84
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,439
